[Episode 32]

19
00:01:39,020 --> 00:01:40,350
[Grand Commandant's Residence]

20
00:01:40,350 --> 00:01:41,440
Please.

21
00:01:43,660 --> 00:01:44,150
Please.

22
00:01:47,800 --> 00:01:48,510
Mr. Zhou.

23
00:01:48,630 --> 00:01:49,360
Mr. Wang.

24
00:01:49,480 --> 00:01:50,510
How have you been?

25
00:01:50,510 --> 00:01:51,080
Yes.

26
00:01:51,080 --> 00:01:52,080
It's been a long time.

27
00:01:52,360 --> 00:01:53,800
Mr. Sun, please.

28
00:01:54,630 --> 00:01:55,510
Mr. Sun.

29
00:01:55,630 --> 00:01:56,830
Please...

30
00:01:56,950 --> 00:01:58,630
- Please.
- Please...

31
00:02:08,010 --> 00:02:11,360
Grand Commandant Jia, you look
even more impressive in your armor.

32
00:02:11,550 --> 00:02:13,830
Please support us in the future.

33
00:02:14,030 --> 00:02:16,270
Yes, Grand Commandant Jia.
Please support us.

34
00:02:17,390 --> 00:02:18,160
Grand Commandant Jia.

35
00:02:18,720 --> 00:02:22,270
No, we should be calling you
Grand Marshal now.

36
00:02:24,160 --> 00:02:26,030
Congratulations, Grand Marshal.

37
00:02:26,470 --> 00:02:27,550
Thank you.

38
00:02:30,440 --> 00:02:31,110
Mr. Liu.

39
00:02:31,440 --> 00:02:32,720
It's a great honor

40
00:02:32,720 --> 00:02:34,600
to have you here.

41
00:02:34,670 --> 00:02:37,320
From now on, we will rely on you
to protect the nation

42
00:02:37,320 --> 00:02:39,630
so that the people
will not have to wander away,

43
00:02:39,750 --> 00:02:43,080
and the royalty will not
have to endure suffering.

44
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:45,440
I will spare no effort

45
00:02:45,600 --> 00:02:46,750
to achieve this.

46
00:02:50,670 --> 00:02:51,910
Isn't this Mr. Pan?

47
00:02:52,270 --> 00:02:53,240
He is...

48
00:02:54,670 --> 00:02:57,240
Mr. Pan has a good reputation,

49
00:02:58,360 --> 00:02:59,880
but it's a pity

50
00:02:59,960 --> 00:03:01,800
that he has a son who's not good enough.

51
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:04,270
And he's been suspended.

52
00:03:04,910 --> 00:03:06,880
I feel sorry for him,

53
00:03:07,160 --> 00:03:09,080
so I'll let him show his loyalty

54
00:03:09,390 --> 00:03:10,800
to the Empress.

55
00:03:20,270 --> 00:03:22,360
I know you're still thinking about Jing.

56
00:03:23,830 --> 00:03:24,960
But today

57
00:03:25,030 --> 00:03:26,470
is your husband's big day.

58
00:03:26,750 --> 00:03:28,240
I've come here to keep you company.

59
00:03:29,080 --> 00:03:31,520
You should take good care of yourself.

60
00:03:34,500 --> 00:03:38,940
[Grand Commandant's Residence]

61
00:03:41,960 --> 00:03:43,630
The ceremony is about to begin.

62
00:03:44,080 --> 00:03:45,360
Why isn't Jiang here yet?

63
00:04:19,880 --> 00:04:22,230
Are you Bai Xiaosheng?

64
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:25,200
Yes, it's me.

65
00:04:49,830 --> 00:04:52,000
He asked me to find Bai Xiaosheng.

66
00:04:55,510 --> 00:04:57,110
Tell her

67
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:59,200
that I want...

68
00:05:02,200 --> 00:05:04,440
I want to go back

69
00:05:09,230 --> 00:05:11,640
to the side of my best friend
I've ever had.

70
00:05:15,320 --> 00:05:16,350
Okay?

71
00:05:21,980 --> 00:05:25,180
♪Looking back, it's autumn♪

72
00:05:25,220 --> 00:05:28,500
♪Whose gentle tears fall?♪

73
00:05:28,900 --> 00:05:34,580
♪Your heart is troubled,
your sigh filled with love and sorrow♪

74
00:05:35,660 --> 00:05:38,980
♪You look back, your life's wish♪

75
00:05:39,020 --> 00:05:42,580
♪For whom you are playing this tune?♪

76
00:05:42,780 --> 00:05:49,220
♪I saw through the parting
between life and death♪

77
00:05:49,380 --> 00:05:56,140
♪The dream of reincarnation,
I'm seeing you off again in my heart♪

78
00:05:56,380 --> 00:05:59,100
♪I am still thinking of you
in another life♪

79
00:05:59,300 --> 00:06:02,980
♪How passionate your love is♪

80
00:06:03,340 --> 00:06:06,380
♪The pain of reincarnation♪

81
00:06:06,540 --> 00:06:10,100
♪Tore apart the heaviness of the cage♪

82
00:06:10,180 --> 00:06:12,620
♪I ring the bell of reincarnation♪

83
00:06:12,820 --> 00:06:17,860
♪And look forward
to embracing you again♪

84
00:06:31,420 --> 00:06:34,620
♪Looking back, it's autumn♪

85
00:06:34,780 --> 00:06:38,020
♪Whose gentle tears fall?♪

86
00:06:38,420 --> 00:06:44,100
♪Your heart is troubled,
your sigh filled with love and sorrow♪

87
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:49,000
Here's a trick for you.

88
00:06:49,390 --> 00:06:50,670
Whenever you're sad,

89
00:06:51,160 --> 00:06:52,950
you can have something sweet.

90
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:55,950
The sweetness in your mouth

91
00:06:56,440 --> 00:06:57,550
will wash away the sadness.

92
00:06:58,900 --> 00:07:02,020
♪The pain of reincarnation♪

93
00:07:02,140 --> 00:07:05,660
♪Tore apart the heaviness of the cage♪

94
00:07:05,740 --> 00:07:08,260
♪I ring the bell of reincarnation♪

95
00:07:08,380 --> 00:07:13,620
♪And look forward
to embracing you again♪

96
00:07:13,860 --> 00:07:24,260
♪The pain of reincarnation
is a dream planted in the past life♪

97
00:07:28,830 --> 00:07:30,200
Promotion announcement.

98
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:43,640
By order of the Emperor,
I am here to deliver a decree.

99
00:07:44,440 --> 00:07:45,830
Jia Quan, listen to the decree.

100
00:07:55,110 --> 00:07:56,480
The Grand Commandant, Jia Quan.

101
00:07:56,880 --> 00:07:59,950
He is a man of virtue and clear mind,

102
00:08:00,110 --> 00:08:02,670
who has been entrusted with authority
for more than a decade

103
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:04,760
and still shoulders the burden
of protecting the country.

104
00:08:05,390 --> 00:08:07,070
He undertakes the responsibility

105
00:08:07,510 --> 00:08:08,830
of preaching and spreading

106
00:08:09,070 --> 00:08:12,070
my benevolence
and righteousness all over the world.

107
00:08:12,670 --> 00:08:15,230
I hereby appoint Jia Quan
as Grand Marshal

108
00:08:15,790 --> 00:08:19,160
and authorize him to assume
command of the three armies.

109
00:08:20,880 --> 00:08:21,950
Accept the decree.

110
00:08:30,510 --> 00:08:31,720
Thank you, Your Majesty.

111
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:34,960
Long live, Your Majesty.

112
00:08:42,790 --> 00:08:45,080
Bring up the Golden Seal
with Purple Shade.

113
00:08:49,800 --> 00:08:51,360
Bring up the Tiger Token.

114
00:09:05,280 --> 00:09:06,350
Receive it.

115
00:09:07,110 --> 00:09:08,150
Hold on!

116
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:09,840
- What...
- What...

117
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:11,400
What's going on?

118
00:09:14,780 --> 00:09:15,400
[The Late Princess Changle,
Liu's Memorial Tablet]

119
00:09:15,400 --> 00:09:16,880
What's Pan Yue doing here?

120
00:09:17,150 --> 00:09:18,420
This is Princess Changle's
memorial tablet.

121
00:09:18,420 --> 00:09:19,260
Who dares show disrespect?

122
00:09:21,140 --> 00:09:22,660
[The Late Princess Changle,
Liu's Memorial Tablet]

123
00:09:23,400 --> 00:09:23,980
Princess Changle?

124
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:25,080
You're fugitives!

125
00:09:25,150 --> 00:09:26,640
How dare you break into
my residence with a weapon?

126
00:09:26,710 --> 00:09:27,910
Take them down!

127
00:09:28,760 --> 00:09:29,520
Your Majesty,

128
00:09:30,400 --> 00:09:32,110
there's another cause
for Princess Changle's death.

129
00:09:32,880 --> 00:09:34,670
The real culprit
is related to an enemy spy.

130
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:36,960
Your Majesty, I hope you'll
allow me to present my defense

131
00:09:37,470 --> 00:09:40,280
so that the princess can rest in peace.

132
00:09:41,710 --> 00:09:43,200
An enemy spy?

133
00:09:47,470 --> 00:09:48,110
Your Majesty,

134
00:09:48,400 --> 00:09:51,110
they are trying to clear their names
by obfuscating the issue.

135
00:09:51,790 --> 00:09:54,910
Today is the Grand Marshal's
conferral ceremony.

136
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:57,550
Don't let the two of them

137
00:09:57,640 --> 00:09:58,790
delay the auspicious time.

138
00:09:58,960 --> 00:09:59,880
I suggest

139
00:09:59,960 --> 00:10:01,710
that they be sent to jail

140
00:10:01,790 --> 00:10:03,000
and be tried after that.

141
00:10:03,910 --> 00:10:05,230
Your Majesty!

142
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:11,110
Father.

143
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:18,400
Your Majesty,
the conferral ceremony is important,

144
00:10:19,200 --> 00:10:21,440
but it's about an enemy spy.

145
00:10:22,230 --> 00:10:24,520
It's not a trifle, Your Majesty.

146
00:10:28,030 --> 00:10:28,840
I am

147
00:10:29,790 --> 00:10:33,400
willing to put my life on the line

148
00:10:33,880 --> 00:10:35,000
to beg you

149
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:38,880
to give him another chance
to explain himself, Your Majesty.

150
00:10:49,590 --> 00:10:50,790
Come forward and talk.

151
00:10:54,520 --> 00:10:56,320
Thank you, Your Majesty.

152
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:18,230
Yang Caiwei committed a murder

153
00:11:18,280 --> 00:11:19,110
and escaped from jail.

154
00:11:19,440 --> 00:11:21,910
The evidence is completely concrete.

155
00:11:22,880 --> 00:11:24,520
What else can you claim?

156
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:27,150
In order to uncover the spy
in the court,

157
00:11:27,710 --> 00:11:29,280
the princess went out of her way
to ruin her reputation

158
00:11:29,520 --> 00:11:30,790
by pretending to be engaged to me.

159
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:33,400
She was eventually forced
to commit suicide.

160
00:11:33,550 --> 00:11:36,110
That's how the spy

161
00:11:36,320 --> 00:11:37,470
set up Yang Caiwei

162
00:11:37,710 --> 00:11:38,880
to stop us from investigating.

163
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:41,280
This is not a love murder

164
00:11:41,670 --> 00:11:43,840
but a well-planned conspiracy.

165
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:51,110
That's impossible.

166
00:11:51,400 --> 00:11:52,470
I know Jing well.

167
00:11:52,960 --> 00:11:55,080
No one could make her do anything
she didn't want to do.

168
00:11:55,760 --> 00:11:58,760
Let's not even talk about whether or not
her engagement to you was real.

169
00:11:59,520 --> 00:12:01,590
What kind of person could force her
to take her own life?

170
00:12:02,080 --> 00:12:02,760
The spy

171
00:12:03,470 --> 00:12:05,350
used your life

172
00:12:05,840 --> 00:12:08,150
to force the princess to give in.

173
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:13,590
Who's the person you're talking about?

174
00:12:14,880 --> 00:12:16,470
"The incident at Qixia Ridge
was due to the spouse."

175
00:12:17,790 --> 00:12:19,790
These are the last words
of the princess.

176
00:12:21,150 --> 00:12:22,470
The person who forced her
to commit suicide

177
00:12:23,030 --> 00:12:24,110
and the one who killed

178
00:12:24,110 --> 00:12:25,710
General Liu and his wife in Luoxi

179
00:12:27,200 --> 00:12:28,840
is your spouse,

180
00:12:30,440 --> 00:12:31,520
the Grand Commandant, Jia Quan.

181
00:12:33,200 --> 00:12:34,400
His true identity

182
00:12:34,880 --> 00:12:36,200
is a spy of the Jiang clan.

183
00:12:36,760 --> 00:12:37,640
Spy?

184
00:12:38,110 --> 00:12:39,640
That's a load of nonsense!

185
00:12:42,790 --> 00:12:44,200
Ten years ago,

186
00:12:44,280 --> 00:12:45,960
my father received
a whistleblowing letter

187
00:12:46,520 --> 00:12:48,320
reporting an enemy spy in the court.

188
00:12:49,280 --> 00:12:50,710
My father was killed

189
00:12:50,980 --> 00:12:52,120
for investigating this matter.

190
00:12:52,460 --> 00:12:53,470
I've been living in obscurity in Heyang

191
00:12:54,030 --> 00:12:55,960
for the past ten years.

192
00:12:56,410 --> 00:12:57,800
When Pan Yue sought me for marriage,

193
00:12:59,300 --> 00:13:01,110
the enemy spy sent someone
to assassinate me.

194
00:13:01,750 --> 00:13:02,880
However, they accidentally

195
00:13:02,880 --> 00:13:04,960
killed Shangguan Zhi,
who was impersonating me.

196
00:13:05,960 --> 00:13:07,470
Pan Yue and I investigated and found out

197
00:13:08,280 --> 00:13:10,110
that the enemy spy
established an influence

198
00:13:10,400 --> 00:13:12,080
to smuggle halite into Heyang.

199
00:13:13,340 --> 00:13:16,300
[Maintaining the Peace]

200
00:13:22,310 --> 00:13:24,570
He joined hands
with the brothel, Shiluo Garden,

201
00:13:24,570 --> 00:13:25,800
for the exchange of power and sex.

202
00:13:25,980 --> 00:13:26,980
[Custom Clearance Document]
They got the Custom Clearance Document

203
00:13:27,960 --> 00:13:29,670
to smuggle halite to the Northwest

204
00:13:30,850 --> 00:13:31,870
and sell it at a low price,

205
00:13:32,230 --> 00:13:34,230
causing the Northwestern army
to have no pay.

206
00:13:34,280 --> 00:13:35,400
That triggered a mutiny.

207
00:13:36,110 --> 00:13:38,550
He ultimately framed General Lu with it.

208
00:13:39,400 --> 00:13:41,080
And the ultimate beneficiary of all this

209
00:13:41,640 --> 00:13:42,720
is Jia Quan.

210
00:13:43,230 --> 00:13:44,720
He took the opportunity
to seize the military power

211
00:13:45,240 --> 00:13:46,420
to make it easy for the Jiang clan

212
00:13:46,720 --> 00:13:47,970
to invade.

213
00:13:49,590 --> 00:13:51,350
How eloquent you are.

214
00:13:51,520 --> 00:13:53,230
You're full of righteousness.

215
00:13:53,640 --> 00:13:54,200
Pan Yue,

216
00:13:54,760 --> 00:13:56,280
you just heard the words "Qixia Ridge"

217
00:13:56,400 --> 00:13:58,030
from the princess,

218
00:13:58,280 --> 00:13:59,430
and you made up

219
00:13:59,550 --> 00:14:01,200
such an outrageous story.

220
00:14:01,960 --> 00:14:02,400
I know

221
00:14:02,920 --> 00:14:04,360
you're still in love

222
00:14:04,360 --> 00:14:05,230
with Miss Yang.

223
00:14:05,440 --> 00:14:06,550
You went to great lengths

224
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:08,400
to get her off the hook.

225
00:14:09,080 --> 00:14:10,320
But I don't get it.

226
00:14:10,550 --> 00:14:11,710
In Heyang,

227
00:14:11,760 --> 00:14:13,200
you have the reputation
of being a great magistrate.

228
00:14:13,710 --> 00:14:15,550
Why can't you distinguish
between right and wrong

229
00:14:15,910 --> 00:14:17,550
for the sake of a witch?

230
00:14:20,280 --> 00:14:20,880
Your Majesty,

231
00:14:21,440 --> 00:14:22,910
they're blatantly slandering

232
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:24,880
a high-ranking official
without evidence.

233
00:14:25,200 --> 00:14:27,080
They should be executed
according to the law.

234
00:14:27,790 --> 00:14:28,960
Rules and discipline
must not be abrogated,

235
00:14:29,030 --> 00:14:30,350
and the order of the country
must not be disrupted.

236
00:14:30,710 --> 00:14:33,320
Your Majesty,
please decree an immediate execution.

237
00:14:33,960 --> 00:14:36,030
Mr. Sun, how do you know
I have no evidence?

238
00:14:36,880 --> 00:14:38,230
Do you really think

239
00:14:38,760 --> 00:14:40,640
you've destroyed all the evidence?

240
00:14:44,110 --> 00:14:44,840
Your Majesty,

241
00:14:45,440 --> 00:14:46,880
please allow me to present the witness.

242
00:14:55,840 --> 00:14:57,280
Come in.

243
00:14:59,060 --> 00:15:05,300
[High Aspiration]

244
00:15:20,520 --> 00:15:22,350
Greetings, Your Majesty.

245
00:15:32,790 --> 00:15:33,910
My name is Yunchang.

246
00:15:34,350 --> 00:15:36,220
I am a performer at Shiluo Garden.

247
00:15:37,200 --> 00:15:38,080
I am also the one

248
00:15:38,280 --> 00:15:39,840
who wrote the whistleblowing letter
to Mr. Yang.

249
00:15:40,640 --> 00:15:41,670
Ten years ago,

250
00:15:42,470 --> 00:15:44,000
it was the first time I met Jia Quan.

251
00:15:55,620 --> 00:15:57,060
[Secret Letter]

252
00:15:59,760 --> 00:16:01,150
Why did you come back here?

253
00:16:02,110 --> 00:16:03,320
We've got

254
00:16:03,640 --> 00:16:06,280
the letter of the spy official
in communication with the enemy.

255
00:16:06,350 --> 00:16:07,030
Besides...

256
00:16:08,710 --> 00:16:11,350
Besides, he's very powerful in Heyang.

257
00:16:11,790 --> 00:16:13,000
When we were discovered,

258
00:16:13,200 --> 00:16:14,150
we were afraid we'd be silenced,

259
00:16:14,590 --> 00:16:15,840
so we had to run away at night

260
00:16:16,150 --> 00:16:17,440
to talk to you about what to do.

261
00:16:17,840 --> 00:16:19,760
I knew Jia Quan wouldn't let us go,

262
00:16:20,470 --> 00:16:21,720
so I wrote to Mr. Yang,

263
00:16:22,280 --> 00:16:24,650
hoping he'd bring Jia Quan down.

264
00:16:25,790 --> 00:16:26,880
But not long after,

265
00:16:27,400 --> 00:16:29,110
we heard the news
that Mr. Yang had been demoted

266
00:16:29,470 --> 00:16:31,460
and killed on his way to exile.

267
00:16:32,620 --> 00:16:33,400
That's when we realized

268
00:16:33,870 --> 00:16:35,280
how powerful this man is.

269
00:16:35,990 --> 00:16:37,160
He has absolute authority.

270
00:16:38,350 --> 00:16:40,720
We'd been living in seclusion in Heyang
ever since.

271
00:16:41,720 --> 00:16:42,760
But soon after,

272
00:16:43,280 --> 00:16:45,110
Jia Quan found out where we were

