633
00:43:32,230 --> 00:43:33,630
Zhuo Lanjiang.

634
00:43:35,120 --> 00:43:36,600
You're pretty smart. Good teamwork.

635
00:43:41,710 --> 00:43:42,910
Don't worry. I'm here.

636
00:43:43,080 --> 00:43:43,870
You'll be fine.

637
00:43:44,120 --> 00:43:45,950
Oh, right. Little Liar...

638
00:43:51,860 --> 00:43:54,940
